<html lang="en"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="./login_files/jquery.min.js.下载"></script>
    <title> login </title>

    <style type="text/css">

        body {
            background: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% auto;
        }

        #Login-box {
            width: 30%;
            height: auto;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 15%;
            text-align: center;
            background: #00000090;
            padding: 20px 50px;
        }

        #Login-box h1 {
            color: #fff;
        }

        #Login-box .form .item {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        #Login-box .form .item i {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        #Login-box .form .item input {
            width: 180px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background: #ffffff00;
            color: #fff;
        }

        #Login-box button {
            margin-top: 15px;
            width: 180px;
            height: 30px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #ab3125 0%, #578bc3 100%);
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>
<div id="Login-box">
    <h1>Login</h1>
    <div class="form">
        <div class="item">
            <i></i>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="用户名：">
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <i></i>
            <input type="text" id="password" name="password" placeholder="密码：">
        </div>
    </div>

    <button id="login" type="button">Login</button>
</div>
<script>

</script>

<script>
    let student = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("student"))
    if (student != null) {
        window.location.href = "BuyBookList.html";
    }
    $("#login").click(function () {
        let username = $('#username').val();
        let password = $('#password').val();
        $.ajax({
            //请求方式
            type: "get",
            //请求的媒体类型
            contentType: "application/json;charset=UTF-8",
            dataType: "json",
            //请求地址
            url: "student/selectOne",
            //数据，json字符串
            data: {sno: username, uname: password},
            //请求成功
            success: function (result) {
                if (result.success === 200) {
                    localStorage.setItem("student", JSON.stringify(result.data))
                    let student = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("student"))
                    window.location.href = "BuyBookList.html";
                    console.log(student);
                } else {
                    alert(result.message)
                }

            },
            //请求失败，包含具体的错误信息
            error: function (e) {
                console.log(e.status);
                console.log(e.responseText);
            }
        });
    });


</script>
